{"result": {"folders": ["lecture17"], "nr": 832, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2016-04-25T06:44:08Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"uid": "i0b2fq3ezjw50r", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-25T06:44:08Z", "data": "infn1nm35pq3rf", "type": "create"}, {"to": "infn1nm0fu43re", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-25T08:23:28Z", "data": "infqlemysal11f", "type": "i_answer"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "i0b2fq3ezjw50r", "subject": "为什么原子锁会导致饥饿&#xff1f;", "created": "2016-04-25T06:44:08Z", "content": "<p>如果原子锁的等待队列也是FIFO的话&#xff0c;这样除了可用资源的限制&#xff0c;跟信号量有什么区别呢&#xff1f;</p>\n<p>为什么MOOC上说原子锁会饥饿&#xff1f;</p>"}], "type": "question", "tags": ["lecture17", "student"], "tag_good": [], "unique_views": 120, "children": [{"folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "children": [], "created": "2016-04-25T08:23:28Z", "bucket_order": 3, "tag_endorse": [], "bucket_name": "Today", "id": "infqlemwmu111e", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "subject": "", "created": "2016-04-25T08:23:28Z", "content": "<p>当使用自旋锁进行临界区访问控制时&#xff0c;并不能保证FIFO的。在Linux等通用操作系统&#xff0c;等待队列也会由于内核可能调整队列顺序而不能保证是FIFO的。于是&#xff0c;会出现饥饿。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>通常锁是内核同步机制&#xff0c;并没有提供相关的系统调用给用户态进程使用&#xff1b;而信号量通常用于用户态&#xff0c;它是基于内核同步机制实现。</p>"}], "type": "i_answer", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "config": {}, "is_tag_endorse": false}], "tag_good_arr": [], "no_answer": 0, "id": "infn1nm0fu43re", "config": {}, "status": "active", "drafts": null, "request_instructor": 0, "request_instructor_me": false, "bookmarked": 4, "num_favorites": 0, "my_favorite": false, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "q_edits": [], "i_edits": [], "s_edits": [], "t": 1643168588712, "default_anonymity": "no"}, "error": null, "aid": "kyv05hgoyfk35f"}